{"tid":1672773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國貨櫃藏屍案39名死者全部是中國人","createTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T11:08:34.000Z","uid":41404,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5e42be5df196fd1cc01b0912b6be0485f137b772","tid":1672773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"英國當局繼續調查貨櫃車內發現39具遺體的案件，英國有傳媒引述消息報道，死者全部是中國人。警方派員搜查北愛爾蘭兩處地方，相信與被捕的北愛爾蘭25歲貨櫃車司機有關連。<br />\n<br />\n警方形容事件是悲劇，首要工作是確認死者身分，預計過程漫長。<br />\n<br />\n警方說涉案車輛在保加利亞註冊，拖頭是從比利時的澤布魯日登上渡輪，在英國時間星期三凌晨零時30分，抵達英國東部埃塞克斯地區的瑟羅克市。警方在貨櫃內發現39名死者，當中包括1名未成年人。男司機涉嫌謀殺被捕。專責打擊犯罪的部門說，會派員協助警方調查案件是否涉及有組織罪案。"},{"pid":"b57532ad4a080c732544bc261297259bad92f3bd","tid":1672773,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488038-20191024.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488038-20191024.htm&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUocRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=11bae0a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488038-20191024.htm&h=f40b20aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488038-20191024.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b925a3c8d84bfd7208fc123d132a2ab951fbdae8","tid":1672773,"uid":277415,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:10.000Z","msg":"1400000000-39"},{"pid":"1ab9ceddddccb5c0898272ff33ff2f987f1bb2ac","tid":1672773,"uid":146724,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"太少了"},{"pid":"fa412289f7986ed8c7035034e036c05aeb8ca725","tid":1672773,"uid":241810,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"At least they died in the UK."},{"pid":"fb2657c8919743f2228656521ff9c251be782639","tid":1672773,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime